These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, western
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person watching western movies is not to the right of the person watching western movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Movie-Genre   | western | superhero |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
City: san-francisco, berlin
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is not to the left of the person traveling to berlin##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| City   | berlin | san-francisco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, malaysian
1. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the malaysian##5
2. the malaysian is on the left or right of the colombian##3
3. the colombian is not to the right of the colombian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Nationality   | colombian | malaysian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
